|_|_|_RepartitionExec: partitioning=Hash([customer_id@1], 20), input_partitions=20 REDACTED
|_|_|_ProjectionExec: expr=[id@0 as id, customer_id@1 as customer_id, amount@2 as amount] REDACTED
|_|_|_MergeScanExec: REDACTED
|_|_|_RepartitionExec: partitioning=Hash([customer_id@0], 20), input_partitions=20 REDACTED
|_|_|_FilterExec: tier@2 = gold REDACTED
|_|_|_ProjectionExec: expr=[customer_id@0 as customer_id, name@1 as name, tier@2 as tier] REDACTED
|_|_|_MergeScanExec: REDACTED
|_|_|_|
| 1_| 0_|_CooperativeExec REDACTED
|_|_|_SeqScan: region=4398046511104(1024, 0), "partition_count":REDACTED REDACTED
|_|_|_|
| 1_| 0_|_CooperativeExec REDACTED
|_|_|_SeqScan: region=4402341478400(1025, 0), "partition_count":REDACTED REDACTED
